ReturnPolicy.Description:
We offer returns with a refund or exchange as long as the following points have been adhered to.

The item(s) needs to be returned: 
- Within 30 days of delivery; 
- Unused with the original tags still attached; and
- In the original packaging and in the original condition.

Please note: Our carrier will deliver your item to your nominated address and a signature is required on delivery. If nobody is there to sign for the parcel, the carrier will leave a card for you to arrange a re-delivery time. If you do not arrange a re-delivery time with the carrier and the item is then returned to us, a $20 re-stocking fee may apply and would be debited from the refund amount. If the sunglasses or glasses case arrives back to us damaged, we will deduct $10 from the refund amount.
